dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipalities for Winnebago County, Wisconsin in 2015. [Corporate boundaries for Winnebago Co., WI. Includes county, city,township and village boundaries . Used by planning, zoning, highway, property lister, 911, andemergency government departments, and also the public and private sector. The corporate boundary file was saved to a file called gm_mcd.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
